<i>noun</i>: 拷問, 고문 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>拷問, 고문</dt><br>
<dd>the deliberate, systematic, or wanton infliction of physical or mental suffering by one or more persons in an attempt to force another person to yield information or to make a confession or for any other reason</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: torture, torturing</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
